WEBVTT

00:00:01.024 --> 00:00:04.291
nokh in geto, in, in KRAKOW

00:00:02.020 --> 00:00:02.891
yo

00:00:04.129 --> 00:00:04.882
yo

00:00:04.990 --> 00:00:11.295
un vi lang, fun velkhe yor biz velkhe yor iz dos azoy umgefer gegangen?

00:00:09.462 --> 00:00:10.555
geganen

00:00:10.555 --> 00:00:13.491
umgega- UNK zenen mir arayngekumen

00:00:13.491 --> 00:00:16.037
BEGIN fertsik

00:00:16.313 --> 00:00:19.665
iz ze'mir geblibn biz ende eyn un fertsik.

00:00:19.536 --> 00:00:22.247
un ir gedenkt AKTIONEN

00:00:21.595 --> 00:00:25.875
yo, zikher. yedes mol gevezn AKTIONEN. gevezn aza plats

00:00:26.269 --> 00:00:29.809
un oyf dem plats hot men tsuzamengenumen nebekh di mentshn.

00:00:29.809 --> 00:00:31.682
m'hot opgeshnitn a shtik geto.

00:00:31.682 --> 00:00:33.032
der vos hot gehat

00:00:33.032 --> 00:00:38.345
ARBEITSKARTE iz geganen dort, hot zikh gemuzt arayn⟨UNK⟩ bay di andere mentshn

00:00:38.658 --> 00:00:41.302
farklenern. m'hot gehat tsvey shtubn, iz men geganen in di

00:00:41.302 --> 00:00:43.948
d- eynem gegebn a shtub un tsveytn gegebn a shtub

00:00:43.988 --> 00:00:46.378
az zey hobn farklenert yedes mol dos geto

00:00:46.722 --> 00:00:50.006
un, un m'hot nebekh di mentshn avekgeshikt.

00:00:49.759 --> 00:00:52.996
un loyt vos iz gegangen dos? iz geven a

00:00:52.996 --> 00:00:55.743
a, a seyder mit, mit

00:00:52.999 --> 00:00:54.630
yekes, dos

00:00:54.973 --> 00:00:56.750
neyn, dos iz gevezn fun

00:00:56.750 --> 00:01:01.476
⟨A PROPRE⟩ hobn zey gemakht ale yontoyvim. s'iz gevezn a peysekh, s'iz gevezn a rosheshone

00:01:01.476 --> 00:01:07.187
azoy ale yontoyvim hobn zey epes gemakht. zey hobn gevust ven iz a yontev, zey hobn gevust az ale mentshn zenen do

00:01:07.187 --> 00:01:08.990
hobn zey UNK dos tog gemakht.

00:01:09.081 --> 00:01:14.154
ikh hob gehat a kuzine vos nebekh iz zi gevezn, iz geganen oyf di arishe papirn

00:01:14.430 --> 00:01:15.824
un m'hot zi gekhapt

00:01:15.915 --> 00:01:18.114
oyf di GRODZKI in kriminal arayn.

00:01:18.114 --> 00:01:26.456
un ikh fun geto, mayn mame hot gekokht, un ikh fun geto bin ikh yedn tog geforn mit esn tsu ir in kriminal arayn.

00:01:27.306 --> 00:01:29.696
zi hot mir aroysgeshikt di shikh

00:01:29.854 --> 00:01:33.864
zi hot gezitsn nebekh ⟨geplekt⟩ di shikh, hot zi mir gemakht di shikh, iz aroysge-

00:01:33.887 --> 00:01:40.879
gevezn a meydl fun akhtsn yor. zi hot zikh gevolt bahaltn oyf arishe papirn, iz zi iz ge- arumgeganen, vayl zi iz gevezn a blonde, a gute

00:01:40.879 --> 00:01:44.698
oyszen un k- gut poylish geredt. ⟨SACHA⟩ hot men zi geheysn.

00:01:45.430 --> 00:01:51.670
un nebekh, un zi hot, m'hot zi genumen ⟨iz⟩ baym ershtn transport vos ⟨iz⟩ takesh geganen di oyszidlung, hot men gebrengt di

00:01:51.670 --> 00:01:55.800
ale yidn vos zenen gevezn oyf di arishe bahaltn dort in kriminal

00:01:55.800 --> 00:01:58.248
hot men zey gebrengt tsu dem ershtn transport.

00:01:58.390 --> 00:02:01.860
vos hobn di mentshn gemeynt, vu, vu brengt men zey?

00:02:01.731 --> 00:02:08.542
zey hobn gemeynt az me geyt tsu di arbet, vayl keyner hot nisht gegleybt az m'hot dokh nisht gevust az s'iz do a oyvn, az me brent.

00:02:08.667 --> 00:02:11.614
zey hobn gezogt me geyt tsu di arbet, un dos iz dos.

00:02:12.261 --> 00:02:15.630
m'iz gevezn azoy vi, ikh ken mikh nisht oysdrikn

00:02:16.024 --> 00:02:21.104
m'hot gornisht farshtanen az, az s'iz dort a krematoryum, az dos geyt alts in oyvn arayn

00:02:21.104 --> 00:02:27.576
⟨vayl⟩ MAJDANEK iz, hot shoyn oykhet, TREBLINKA hot shoyn oykhet gehat a krematoryum shoyn demolts in Poyln. dos iz dort ergets bay Lemberg

00:02:27.580 --> 00:02:29.501
veys nisht vu dos ligt iber hoypt.

00:02:29.980 --> 00:02:34.665
un v- v- m'hot bakumen post fun di mentshn vos m'hot oysgezidlt?

00:02:32.578 --> 00:02:33.739
gornisht.

00:02:33.739 --> 00:02:35.980
gornisht hot men gehat keyn post.

00:02:35.980 --> 00:02:39.860
eyn mol in geto iz epes gekumen a yid

00:02:40.898 --> 00:02:43.423
un kh'veys nisht vi azoy, nor

00:02:43.632 --> 00:02:47.777
ikh bin ts- tsugevoynt fun di heym vos m'hot mir arayngenumen mentshn

00:02:48.424 --> 00:02:52.552
⟨vayl⟩ in Kroke hot men bay undz oykhet stabil gevezn mentshn tsu esn

00:02:52.778 --> 00:03:00.849
stabil gevezn mentshn vos ⟨zenen⟩ gevezn bokherim vos zey hobn gelernt in Kroke. iz gevezn fun oyse- fun UNK kleyne shtetl UNK

00:03:00.849 --> 00:03:03.178
un der tate hot zikh oykhet azoy gefirt

00:03:03.178 --> 00:03:13.016
un iz gekumen epes a yid in la- in geto arayn, un er brengt tsu undz in shtub UNK gezogt "vemen ⟨hostu⟩ UNK gevezn opgetun, nisht ongeton, nisht gor

00:03:13.016 --> 00:03:18.708
vemen host gebren- UNK tsu fartseyln fun MAJDANEK, az er iz fun dort antlofn.

00:03:18.850 --> 00:03:23.183
hot er fartseylt, demolts ershte mol hot er fartseylt az s'iz do a krematoryum

00:03:23.183 --> 00:03:27.095
un s'iz do a bitere lage vos me shlogt, vos me harget

00:03:27.557 --> 00:03:30.667
un afile der vos geyt tsu arbet, s'kumt yedes mol

00:03:30.667 --> 00:03:32.717
veyniker mentshn arayn, ⟨vayl⟩ me

00:03:32.717 --> 00:03:33.987
tsvishn vegn

00:03:33.987 --> 00:03:35.620
harget men, shlogt men zey.

00:03:35.620 --> 00:03:41.028
demolts iz, un fun demolts on hot der tate geklert n- a- a- avek antloyfn, antloyfn

00:03:41.028 --> 00:03:44.359
hot er ongehoybn tsu makhn di papirn far undz, far di kinder

00:03:44.905 --> 00:03:49.888
un az s'iz gevezn di oyszidlung, geven z- eyn m- oyszidlung, ⟨ts- dray mol⟩ iz gevezn

00:03:49.888 --> 00:03:54.112
biz m'iz undz geganen in lager arayn. dray mol gevezn oyszidlungen

00:03:54.118 --> 00:03:57.338
az s'iz geven di oyszidlung bay undz, undz ze'mir ale beyde

00:03:57.338 --> 00:04:00.004
avekgelofn UNK ikh mit mayn shvester

00:04:00.004 --> 00:04:01.975
mit di klenere, di gresere nisht

00:04:02.522 --> 00:04:04.542
avekgelofn tsu di goyim.

00:04:04.542 --> 00:04:07.492
der tate hot gehat bakantshaft, azoy az hot gehat

00:04:07.492 --> 00:04:09.352
plats vu undz tsu ⟨plasirn⟩

00:04:09.352 --> 00:04:12.601
ABER a, a nakht nokh dem f-

00:04:12.601 --> 00:04:15.231
oyszidlung zenen mir shoyn tsurikgelofn in geto arayn

00:04:15.251 --> 00:04:19.256
hobn mir nisht gevolt zayn bay di goyim, shreklekh. ershte mol, hot men nisht gekent aroysgeyn.

00:04:19.548 --> 00:04:25.587
shpeter hot g- di moyre iz geven zeyer groys. tomer hot gegebn a klap in di tir, hot men zikh gedarft bahaltn untern bet

00:04:25.587 --> 00:04:31.727
s'iz ge- ⟨shoyn⟩ geven meydlekh fun tsen yor. UNK shoyn farshteyn, s'iz a bitere zakh dos do. s'iz shoyn nisht keyn lebn dos do.

00:04:32.155 --> 00:04:36.199
di klener hot gehat nayn, ikh hob gehat tsen, mayn shvester hot gehat elef, un i-

00:04:36.424 --> 00:04:40.485
un m'hot dokh shoyn gezen az s'iz a ⟨bitere⟩ tsayt, zenen mir bald tsurikgelofn

00:04:40.761 --> 00:04:47.744
un shpeter iz di sh- az di geto hot zikh likvidirt, iz arayngekumen di sh- mayn mame's shvester mit a kind.

00:04:47.744 --> 00:04:50.576
der tate hot arayngenumen di dray kinder

00:04:50.785 --> 00:04:54.266
fun, fun bruder, ale tsu undz in WOHNUNG arayn.

00:04:54.266 --> 00:04:56.595
un der yid iz oykhet arayngekumen

00:04:56.595 --> 00:05:00.955
shoyn on a bord, gornisht, azoy hefker ongetun, iz er oykhet arayngekumen

00:05:00.955 --> 00:05:02.405
tsu undz, hot oykhet fartsey-

00:05:02.405 --> 00:05:04.165
iz oykh geshlofn bay undz.

00:05:04.165 --> 00:05:07.788
far dem zog ikh der tish mit di benklekh iz gevezn undzere betn.

00:05:09.415 --> 00:05:12.598
ven hot zikh far aykh geendert di

00:05:13.161 --> 00:05:15.129
di lage fun di

00:05:15.523 --> 00:05:16.664
geto?

00:05:16.738 --> 00:05:19.670
vos iz pasirt az dos iz

00:05:17.852 --> 00:05:21.187
⟨dos⟩ lage fun di geto iz gevezn azoy.

00:05:21.210 --> 00:05:22.084
az s'hot

00:05:22.084 --> 00:05:30.351
hot likvidirt di, ⟨zi⟩ hot geheysn undz ge- geyen mir alts keyn PLASZOW. langzam hobn zey ongehoybn tsu nemen di mentshn keyn PLASZOW. ⟨me⟩ geyt alts keyn PLASZOW.

00:05:31.285 --> 00:05:39.278
un iz, hot men zikh UNK gemuzt shteln ales, me geyt keyn PLASZOW. vos hot men getrogn oyf zikh, ⟨un⟩ dos iz gevezn, nisht epes andersh.

00:05:39.874 --> 00:05:40.453
a-

00:05:40.453 --> 00:05:42.837
hot der tate dokh gemakht dem bunker

00:05:42.878 --> 00:05:45.336
hot er genumen di dray kinder fun mayn

00:05:45.949 --> 00:05:49.769
fun mayn onkl arayn in bunker arayn. der bunker iz gevezn nor tsu

00:05:49.769 --> 00:05:53.579
knap aniderzetsn zikh oyf a bret. nisht geshlofn, nisht gornisht.

00:05:53.579 --> 00:05:55.910
gevezn azoy di bret un azoy di bret.

00:05:55.910 --> 00:05:59.358
di dray kinder hot er genumen. undz ze'mir geblibn in bunker.

00:05:59.533 --> 00:06:04.272
mayn papir vos ikh hob gehat tsu ARBEITSKARTE

00:06:04.272 --> 00:06:07.562
iz gevezn a bakanter, hot geheysn FAJNER

00:06:07.562 --> 00:06:11.997
in dem zelbn hoyz gehat, hot er gehat a meydl in di zelbe yorn vos ikh

00:06:12.207 --> 00:06:16.633
hot er, der bakanter gevust az der geyt arayn in bunker arayn mit di kinder

00:06:16.633 --> 00:06:19.623
hot er gebetn zol men im gebn mayn papir.

00:06:19.623 --> 00:06:22.813
iz geganen der tate, hot gegebn mayn papir, ⟨vayl⟩ er hot gevust

00:06:22.813 --> 00:06:28.063
az m'vet kenen antlofn, geyn tsu goyim, ⟨vel⟩ ikh dokh geyn tsu goyim. ikh darf dokh nisht dos papir

00:06:28.592 --> 00:06:32.867
un er iz geganen in bunker arayn, nor er eyntsiker hot gevust az undz ze'mir in bunker

00:06:32.867 --> 00:06:35.050
der yid. keyner hot nisht gevust

00:06:35.342 --> 00:06:38.019
iz zenen mir azoy gezesn dort tsvey vokhn.

00:06:38.346 --> 00:06:41.326
un mir hobn zikh ongegreyt tsu esn. vos tsu esn? broyt.

00:06:41.326 --> 00:06:44.166
broyt mit vaser. bay nakht iz ⟨di mame⟩ aroysgeganen

00:06:44.166 --> 00:06:46.666
un zi hot aroysgenumen dos vos hot men gemakht

00:06:46.666 --> 00:06:48.166
un oysgegosn

00:06:48.166 --> 00:06:50.526
un zi hot gebrengt frish a bisele vaser

00:06:50.526 --> 00:06:53.311
un zenen mir ts- fun di kokh, un zenen mir tsurik.

00:06:53.311 --> 00:06:57.374
tsurik arayngeganen un tsugedekt dem bunker. zenen mir azoy gezesn.

00:06:57.374 --> 00:06:59.794
eyn mol bay nakht kumt er tsu geyn

00:06:59.794 --> 00:07:05.064
ruft er "Shloyme." er hot nisht vu iz der plats, nor er hot gevust az s'iz in di shtub. "Shloyme, Shloyme

00:07:05.064 --> 00:07:08.184
du kenst aroysgeyn. efsher geystu aroys

00:07:08.184 --> 00:07:12.336
shpeter vestu zen di familye." zogt er "oh, neyn, ikh gey nisht on mayn familye.

00:07:12.336 --> 00:07:15.839
az du kenst undz nemen ale tsuzamen iz gut

00:07:15.839 --> 00:07:17.709
familye aleyn nisht."

00:07:18.728 --> 00:07:25.168
shpeter iz gevezn nokh di dray kinder oykhet dort in bunker. di dray kinder hobn zey gehat epes a tante

00:07:25.292 --> 00:07:28.917
oykhet, di muter's a shvester. iz gekumen di muter's a shvester

00:07:28.917 --> 00:07:29.769
un zi hot zey

00:07:29.769 --> 00:07:34.821
avekgenumen di dray kinder. azoy zenen mir undz nor geblibn di dray kinder. azoy zenen mir undz nor geblibn di dray kinder, zenen mir azoy gezesn

00:07:35.012 --> 00:07:40.071
hot er gezogt UNK tsun im, vi hot dos geheysn, FAJNER, ober ⟨fun⟩ tsveytn nomen UNK gedenk ikh shoyn nisht

00:07:40.071 --> 00:07:41.615
hot er gezogt "veyst vos?

00:07:41.615 --> 00:07:44.695
efsher kenst mir nokh bazorgn a tsvey broyt.

00:07:44.695 --> 00:07:49.316
ikh veys dokh nisht vi lang ⟨vel⟩ ikh zitsn nokh, dos zoln mir hobn a bisele nokh tsu esn."

00:07:50.048 --> 00:07:55.698
zogt er "sh- leyg mir oyf, untern tish," vayl der tish iz nokh geshtanen in di shtub. "leyg untern tish

00:07:55.698 --> 00:07:59.745
bay nakht, ikh vel ⟨im⟩ aroys, araynnemen," un azoy iz gevezn.

00:07:59.818 --> 00:08:03.912
er iz shoyn gekumen fun PLASZOW arayn in geto arayn

00:08:04.290 --> 00:08:07.250
tsu di KOSZYKARNIA tsu arbet

00:08:07.250 --> 00:08:09.900
vayl s'iz nokh nisht gevezn adurkhgefirt keyn

00:08:10.045 --> 00:08:13.480
keyn, tsum lager arayn, un er iz gekumen, iz azoy iz ge-

00:08:13.480 --> 00:08:17.374
shpeter iz er tsvey tog shpeter tsi dray tog shpeter iz er vider gekumen.

00:08:17.374 --> 00:08:22.194
"Shloyme, di la- di geto iz azoy ⟨arumgeviklt⟩, ikh ho-" geredt

00:08:22.194 --> 00:08:26.394
"azoy arum-" er h- er hot nor gehert di shtime, ober fun vanen hot er nisht gevust fun vanen kum-

00:08:26.394 --> 00:08:30.974
"azoy arumgenumen arum un arum az du vest keyn mol in lebn nisht kenen antloyfn.

00:08:31.358 --> 00:08:35.486
f- gey aroys. gey aroys. vest kenen helfn dayne kinder."

00:08:35.626 --> 00:08:38.956
un er kumt a mol tsu geyn, zogt er azoy. "ikh hob a plats

00:08:38.956 --> 00:08:40.374
in KOSZYKARNIA

00:08:40.374 --> 00:08:42.407
vos a meydl iz antlofn

00:08:42.407 --> 00:08:46.593
z- ⟨ir vet⟩ hobn dayn tokhter di eltste in plats, oyf ir nomen vet zi geyn.

00:08:46.593 --> 00:08:47.214
z-

00:08:47.288 --> 00:08:49.107
undz zoln mir aroysshikn

00:08:49.107 --> 00:08:55.027
a mentshn frier mitn korb, un der mentsh vet azoy makhn,⟨ets vet⟩ zikh nisht meldn, azoy

00:08:55.027 --> 00:08:58.437
az du vest kenen kumen oyfn, dem mentsh's plats, un

00:08:58.459 --> 00:09:01.018
aroyf, aroyfge- i- in lager arayn."

00:09:01.159 --> 00:09:03.822
un azoy hot zikh der tate detsidirt.

00:09:03.822 --> 00:09:07.512
"un vos vet zayn mit di ts- tsvey andere, mit di dray andere

00:09:07.512 --> 00:09:09.012
ikh vel shoyn erleydikn."

00:09:09.175 --> 00:09:14.046
hot er gezogt azoy vider. "iz do a korb vos fort mit vesh aroyf keyn PLASZOW

00:09:14.187 --> 00:09:17.449
⟨vel⟩ ikh araynleygn di kleyne in dem korb arayn"

00:09:17.449 --> 00:09:21.889
un oyf dem ko- fun VORNE iz gezetsn, oyfn kotsh iz gezesn der S.S. man

00:09:21.889 --> 00:09:24.639
un fun hintn iz gezesn ⟨den⟩ yid oyfn korb

00:09:24.639 --> 00:09:29.549
un az m'iz geforn keyn PODGORZE in geto arayn, in lager arayn

00:09:29.549 --> 00:09:32.139
demolts hot er gegebn a sh-

00:09:32.139 --> 00:09:39.180
a gey arunter fun dem korb, un oyfgemakht dem korb ven s'iz geblibn shteyn der vogn, hot zi gegebn a shpring aroys un geganen tsu dem polyak.

00:09:39.516 --> 00:09:45.028
iz zi dort gezesn bay dem polyak, un tsufelik iz nisht gehat azoy shlekht, iz nor nimes gevorn.

00:09:45.439 --> 00:09:48.656
er iz gekumen tsu undz, ⟨vayl⟩ undz ho'mir gegebn a sakh gelt.

00:09:48.392 --> 00:09:50.765
vi iz er tsu aykh gekumen?

00:09:50.518 --> 00:09:52.891
in a f- in lager iz er tsu undz gekumen.

00:09:52.442 --> 00:09:56.708
ir zent shoyn demolts geven in lager. in velkhe lager zent ir geven?

00:09:53.708 --> 00:09:55.406
in lager, iz hot zi

00:09:55.648 --> 00:09:56.806
in PLASZOW.

00:09:56.708 --> 00:09:58.834
vi azoy zent ir dort ongekumen?

00:09:58.737 --> 00:10:02.359
tsu fus, UNK. ⟨dort⟩ iz men geganen tsu fus. s'iz gornisht geven keyn

00:10:01.302 --> 00:10:03.152
ven iz dos geven?

00:10:02.837 --> 00:10:05.548
dos iz gevezn shoyn

00:10:05.706 --> 00:10:07.590
e- ende eyn un fertsik.

00:10:07.950 --> 00:10:12.078
un ver hot aykh dos bafoyln dortn tsu geyn?

00:10:10.937 --> 00:10:16.803
di ge- di yekes, in di ge- di yekes zenen geganen mit undz un azoy mit di bagnetn hot men undz gefirt.

00:10:16.438 --> 00:10:19.807
vayl ir zent dokh geven farshtekt in a bunker.

00:10:18.666 --> 00:10:24.036
neyn. dos iz gevezn UNK di mentshn zenen geganen. ikh bin nokh nisht geganen. ikh bin gevezn nokh in bunker.

00:10:24.036 --> 00:10:25.686
ikh hob dertseylt dos nokh fun bunker.

00:10:25.686 --> 00:10:27.974
undz ze'mir geblibn nokh in bunker

00:10:28.116 --> 00:10:29.730
un shpeter

00:10:30.208 --> 00:10:38.018
un shpeter di shvester hot dort zi dort arayngeleygt in korb arayn, un eyn shvester iz geganen in dem KOSZYKARNIA fabrik, di eltste

00:10:38.018 --> 00:10:41.649
un der tate oykhet. undz, ikh mit di mame, ⟨zenen mir⟩ nokh geblibn

00:10:41.751 --> 00:10:47.280
oyfn vaser, vi me zogt. nisht gehat vu tsu arayntsugeyn. er hot gemeynt epes erleydikn, tsvishn UNK hot er gornisht erleydikt.

00:10:47.505 --> 00:10:50.941
kegn iber undz iz gevezn a shpitol.

00:10:51.302 --> 00:10:55.452
di shpitol iz vider gekumen mentshn likvidirn di shpitol

00:10:55.452 --> 00:10:57.592
un m'hot dos alts ahingefirt keyn

00:10:57.592 --> 00:10:59.332
keyn PLASZOW in geto arayn.

00:10:59.332 --> 00:11:06.231
un azoy iz er geganen un hot erleydikt di mentshn, zoln mir undz mitgeyn dort, ober fun dort iz keyner nisht avek.

00:11:06.557 --> 00:11:09.397
ikh kum keyn PLASZOW mit di mame tsuzamen

00:11:09.397 --> 00:11:12.967
me rekhnt, me nemt mir shoyn tsu mit di mame tsuzamen

00:11:12.967 --> 00:11:13.942
oyf

00:11:13.999 --> 00:11:17.385
oyf di S.S., di kapos

00:11:17.442 --> 00:11:20.468
aza hoyz hobn zey gehat. m'hot undz shoyn dort arayngenumen.

00:11:20.468 --> 00:11:23.072
di moyre iz gevezn azoy groys.

00:11:23.280 --> 00:11:25.518
dos hob ikh shoyn farshtanen demolts, dem

00:11:25.626 --> 00:11:27.376
moyre iz gevezn shreklekh groys

00:11:27.376 --> 00:11:32.426
ABER zenen mir nokh avekgegan- aroysgeganen fun bunker, zenen mir gevezn gel vi vaks

00:11:32.578 --> 00:11:35.899
zenen mir gevezn dort dray vokhn nisht gevashn

00:11:35.899 --> 00:11:37.317
unter erd

00:11:37.317 --> 00:11:39.577
nisht keyn luft, vi vaks zenen mir gevezn.

00:11:39.577 --> 00:11:42.607
kegn mi- iber undz iz gevezn JUSTE a

00:11:42.607 --> 00:11:46.567
a vash ROOM, iz geganen der yid, hot erleydikt

00:11:46.567 --> 00:11:50.323
hot undz ale arayngefirt ⟨tsun im shoyn⟩ in dem vash ROOM, der FAJNER.

00:11:49.234 --> 00:11:51.040
vu iz dos geven?

00:11:50.736 --> 00:11:53.143
in, oyf di JOZEFINSKI, in geto.

00:11:53.773 --> 00:12:00.241
un UNK arayngefirt in dem vash ROOM, hot UNK undz ale opgevashn, zenen mir gevorn andere mentshn. shpeter hot men gekent geyn

00:12:00.241 --> 00:12:02.441
aroyf ts- in keyn lager.

00:12:02.937 --> 00:12:04.887
undz ze'mir geganen mit im

00:12:04.887 --> 00:12:07.157
mit di GROUP fun di vos zenen gekumen

00:12:07.157 --> 00:12:08.607
in di shpitol

00:12:08.607 --> 00:12:09.680
tsu

00:12:10.193 --> 00:12:15.924
tsu likvidirn, un mir ze'mir geganen, zenen gekumen keyn PLASZOW, hot men gezen tsvey mentshn, iz do mer

00:12:16.521 --> 00:12:18.703
un hot men zey undz tsugenumen

00:12:18.703 --> 00:12:22.613
ABER mayn tate iz shoyn gevezn demolts in lager, UNK dos iz gevezn bay nakht.

00:12:22.613 --> 00:12:24.273
er iz shoyn gevezn in lager.

00:12:23.895 --> 00:12:25.610
in dem PLASZOW?

00:12:24.273 --> 00:12:25.503
er

00:12:25.503 --> 00:12:29.373
in PLASZOW, yo. un er hot gezen az undz ze'mir

00:12:29.515 --> 00:12:32.566
oyf di UNK, zitst men dort oyf UNK.

00:12:32.566 --> 00:12:34.464
gelt hot er gehat bay zikh.

00:12:34.464 --> 00:12:36.123
hot er bald genumen UNK

00:12:36.163 --> 00:12:40.522
gefregt zikh vemen ken men dos hit- CHIL- CHILOWICZ hot geheysn der

00:12:40.522 --> 00:12:41.439
kapo

00:12:41.682 --> 00:12:46.699
un FINKELSTEIN iz gevezn der tsveyter. yednfal, hot er ge⟨UNK⟩ a UNK

00:12:46.699 --> 00:12:49.036
tsu dem mentsh, a plats ⟨JEMAND⟩

00:12:49.036 --> 00:12:52.054
un hot gegebn im gelt, hot men zey ⟨aroysgelozt⟩.

00:12:52.161 --> 00:12:55.651
bin ikh geganen in, tsurik in mayn KOSZYKARSKI

00:12:55.651 --> 00:12:57.191
vu ikh hob gearbet

00:12:57.527 --> 00:12:59.968
bin ikh gevezn tsvey LACHNERS.

00:13:00.649 --> 00:13:04.271
dos meydl iz gevezn a LACHNER, un ikh bin gevezn a LACHNER.

00:13:04.277 --> 00:13:08.290
⟨geven⟩ tsvey LACHNERS. UNK oyfmerkzam, ⟨vayl⟩ UNK bald fartseyln vayter.

00:13:08.290 --> 00:13:10.278
iz gevezn tsvey LACHNERS

00:13:10.521 --> 00:13:14.126
undz ze'mir beyde gearbet dort. m'hot undz arayngenumen. far vos?

00:13:14.183 --> 00:13:17.437
iberal gevezn dos zelbe. host gehat gelt

00:13:17.437 --> 00:13:18.879
hostu geganen for.

00:13:18.879 --> 00:13:21.754
host nisht gehat keyn gelt, bistu gevezn biter.

00:13:22.435 --> 00:13:24.988
ober ir zent geven yetst in

00:13:24.988 --> 00:13:26.743
in PLASZOW

00:13:26.743 --> 00:13:29.240
vos far a sort lager iz dos geven?

00:13:26.772 --> 00:13:27.323
yo

00:13:28.948 --> 00:13:32.722
der lager iz gevezn a katset lager

00:13:33.387 --> 00:13:36.958
a ARBEITSLAGER un a rikhtike ka- katset lager.

00:13:36.660 --> 00:13:38.257
un ver iz dort geven?

00:13:37.622 --> 00:13:40.434
dort iz gevezn GOTH.

00:13:41.503 --> 00:13:44.399
GOTH iz gevezn der gantser onfirer.

00:13:44.625 --> 00:13:47.335
un shpeter hot er gehat S.S. man unter zikh

00:13:47.335 --> 00:13:51.455
farshidene S.S. man, iz gevezn a ⟨WILUSZ⟩, a biterer S.S. man

00:13:51.455 --> 00:13:54.711
vos er hot nisht gevust tsi arayngeyn durkh a tir nor durkh a fentster

00:13:54.711 --> 00:13:57.511
vayl s'iz dokh gevezn barakn, un di shpring arayn iz geven s-

00:13:57.511 --> 00:14:01.191
geshlogn, geharget. ikh hob gekrign fun im finef un tsvontsik.

00:14:02.749 --> 00:14:04.903
un s'iz geven yidn

00:14:03.559 --> 00:14:06.725
a kind, a kind gevezn, gekrign fi-

00:14:06.833 --> 00:14:08.362
finef un tsvontsik.

00:14:08.284 --> 00:14:11.585
s'iz geven yidn fun andere pletser dort oykh?

00:14:10.528 --> 00:14:16.360
yo, yo, yo. zikher gevezn yidn vos hot men demolts genumen ales vos hot gemuzt geyn arum un arum

00:14:17.548 --> 00:14:19.410
hot men ale genumen

00:14:19.410 --> 00:14:23.786
keyn PLASZOW vos zenen gevezn in geto. di ale hot men genumen keyn PLASZOW.

00:14:23.252 --> 00:14:25.389
vos hot men dort getun?

00:14:24.619 --> 00:14:30.876
gearbet. alts hot ge- -a- -arbet. s'iz do gevezn a papir, papir g- fabrik. es iz gevezn a

00:14:30.876 --> 00:14:34.918
a n- sh- m'hot geneyt antsiger far di yekes.

00:14:34.918 --> 00:14:41.077
s'iz gevezn ales, kadres, ales vos hot bashi- a shuster iz gevezn. a shnayder iz gevezn vos hot

00:14:41.077 --> 00:14:44.047
ales iz gevezn. gevezn gantse lange barakn

00:14:44.047 --> 00:14:45.367
vos hot men gearbet.

00:14:45.367 --> 00:14:47.684
s'iz gevezn a groyse kokh iz gevezn

00:14:47.684 --> 00:14:50.381
m'iz geshe- gezitsn un gesheylt kartofl.

00:14:50.893 --> 00:14:53.075
vi alt zent ir geven demolts?

00:14:52.868 --> 00:14:55.005
demolts bin ikh gevezn tsvelef yor.

00:14:55.450 --> 00:14:59.072
un zey hobn gegebn oykh far kinder arbet?

00:14:58.150 --> 00:15:01.774
z- ikh bin gevezn keyneynehore zeyer gut ⟨erviklt⟩.

00:15:01.774 --> 00:15:03.239
azoy vi haynt bin ikh.

00:15:03.432 --> 00:15:04.725
far vos?

00:15:04.782 --> 00:15:08.963
⟨vayl⟩ ikh hob gehat ⟨voynen⟩ a bobe in Makev. kh'hob fartseylt dos do

00:15:08.963 --> 00:15:10.625
un fun geto

00:15:10.625 --> 00:15:16.099
bin ikh geforn stabil st- keyn Makev tsu di bobe. far vos? vayl zey hobn nokh nisht gegesn keyn treyfe.

00:15:16.155 --> 00:15:18.056
s'iz gekumen a peysekh

00:15:18.096 --> 00:15:21.819
hot men gefirt matses, hob ikh geforn firn matses.

00:15:22.838 --> 00:15:30.141
m'iz geganen epes dort, ⟨iz⟩ nisht gevezn UNK koshere zakhn, hob ikh fun Kroke gefirt tsu zey koshere zakhn, hin un tsurik, als a goye.

00:15:30.141 --> 00:15:31.674
vayl ikh bin gevezn a blonde

00:15:32.203 --> 00:15:33.702
hob ikh gekent forn.

00:15:33.702 --> 00:15:37.566
un dos iz nisht gevezn laykht tsu forn. dos iz gevezn a tsvey shtundn tsu forn

00:15:37.566 --> 00:15:41.023
biz ikh bin tsugeganen tsu a fentster, gekoyft a tiket

00:15:41.147 --> 00:15:42.975
⟨hob⟩ ikh shoyn gevezn halb toyt

00:15:42.975 --> 00:15:44.887
vayl ikh hob farshtanen ikh bin a yidishe

00:15:45.130 --> 00:15:49.210
un shpeter bin ikh geganen aleyn oyfn tsug bahaltn zikh in a ekl un gezesn

00:15:49.210 --> 00:15:49.986
in tsug

00:15:49.986 --> 00:15:53.290
un do hob ikh gefirt matses, un do bin ikh gevezn a goye

00:15:55.052 --> 00:15:57.712
un mayne bobe zeyde zenen takesh avek

00:15:58.039 --> 00:16:00.491
⟨meg men⟩ zogn, nor s'iz gevezn bashert

00:16:00.491 --> 00:16:07.365
ABER az mayn tate hot gevolt mikh demolt shikn, vos m'hot gevust az s'vet zayn a oy- a oyszidlung yetst in Makev

00:16:08.468 --> 00:16:12.169
un di papirn hot er erleydikt far di bobe zeydes als a goye

00:16:12.169 --> 00:16:16.309
un dos iz gekumen JUSTE fraytik di papir arayn in geto arayn

00:16:17.867 --> 00:16:20.223
papir arayngeyn hot er. ⟨hot⟩ di mame gezogt

00:16:21.450 --> 00:16:25.050
"me shikt dos kind" zogt der tate. "neyn. dos kind vel ikh nisht shikn.

00:16:25.208 --> 00:16:28.661
s'iz do a shabes UNK zi vet forn hersht montik

00:16:29.022 --> 00:16:32.300
vayl s'iz do a shabes. zey kenen makhn shabes di oyszidlung. ikh

00:16:32.300 --> 00:16:34.850
UNK shabes vet zi dokh nisht forn tsurik mitn tsug

00:16:35.265 --> 00:16:37.976
ikh vel nisht shi-" un s'iz takesh azoy gevezn.

00:16:38.573 --> 00:16:42.802
shabes iz gevezn di oyszidlung, UNK az ikh bin dort gevezn, bin ikh gevezn tsvishn

00:16:43.433 --> 00:16:45.536
un di papirn zenen geblibn lign.

00:16:45.897 --> 00:16:50.076
ver iz geven mit aykh in PLASZOW fun ayere familye?

00:16:49.626 --> 00:16:59.509
fun ⟨mayne⟩ familye iz gevezn mayn shvester, di eltste, un tate mame zenen gevezn. iz gevezn mame's a bruder iz gevezn, iz gevezn di shv- di shvester mitn man

00:16:59.667 --> 00:17:01.095
iz gevezn.

00:17:01.540 --> 00:17:05.989
un m'hot dort gemakht AKTIONEN oykhet? s'iz geven ⟨a⟩ aktsye?

00:17:04.392 --> 00:17:10.478
neyn, neyn, dort vider iz gevezn vider az m'hot genumen yedes mol a grupe tsu di arbet.

00:17:10.922 --> 00:17:16.834
m'hot geshikt dan, m'hot gedarft, yekes hobn gedarft do arbet, dort arbet, azoy vi m'hot gedarft a UNK tsu makhn.

00:17:16.834 --> 00:17:21.801
far di mentshn UNK finef hundert mentshn tsu der arbet, iz men gekumen keyn PLASZOW tsu nemen fun dort.

00:17:21.958 --> 00:17:25.445
un s'iz geven, m'hot geharget mentshn dort?

00:17:25.030 --> 00:17:31.453
m'hot geharget, m'hot geshosn, nisht geharg- m'hot gebrengt mentshn fun bunker, hot men sh- geshosn di mentshn. m'hot ge-

00:17:31.645 --> 00:17:35.588
n- az JEMAND hot gevolt antloyfn, hot men bald ⟨an⟩ im geshosn

00:17:35.830 --> 00:17:40.543
un Hitler iz aroysgegan- GOTH heyst dos iz aroysgeganen fun lager

00:17:40.543 --> 00:17:47.315
hot er gehat a tsvey azolkhene groyse hint, azoy vi iz ge- aroysgeganen fun zayn shtub in lager, hot men gevust az s'vet shoyn zayn

00:17:47.338 --> 00:17:49.470
s'vet shoyn zayn a, a

00:17:49.470 --> 00:17:54.369
UNK ⟨JEMAND⟩ shisn, UNK ⟨BESTEHT⟩ arayngeyn tsurik in shtub arayn, zol nisht shisn.

00:17:54.375 --> 00:17:55.565
dos BESTEHT nisht.

00:17:55.565 --> 00:17:56.845
az nisht ⟨zenen⟩ dort gegebn a

00:17:56.845 --> 00:17:58.505
patsh mit, azoy mitn rayt baytsh

00:17:58.505 --> 00:18:00.915
un di hint gegebn a shpring aroyf oyf di mentshn.

00:18:01.142 --> 00:18:02.655
yo, tsu

00:18:01.429 --> 00:18:07.650
UNK er hot afile nisht gedarft redn, nor a patsh gegebn mitn bay- hot shoyn gevust di tsvey hint tsu, tsu tseraysn ⟨dey⟩ mentsh.

00:18:07.369 --> 00:18:09.708
ir hot dos b- gezen di zakh?

00:18:08.533 --> 00:18:11.345
yo, shpeter bin ikh eyn mol gevezn. undz ho'mir

00:18:12.027 --> 00:18:17.577
kh'vel fartseyln vayter UNK ikh halt yetst bay GOTHn UNK redn dos, ikh bin gevezn in

00:18:17.577 --> 00:18:20.607
shpeter hot men undz gefirt fun, zi hot zikh likvidirt di

00:18:20.607 --> 00:18:25.492
KOSZYKARSKIs. m'iz geganen tsu sh- kartofl sheyln. yedes mol hot men undz geshikt ergets vayter.

00:18:25.492 --> 00:18:28.575
bin gevezn baym kartofl sheyln, zenen mir gezesn

00:18:28.733 --> 00:18:30.954
in di geto iz arayngekumen

00:18:31.602 --> 00:18:34.144
m'hot gemakht akhtung. ale hot geshtanen

00:18:34.521 --> 00:18:38.702
iz gesh- iz gezesn bay mir a meydl, hot geheysn Ashkenazi

00:18:38.702 --> 00:18:43.558
sheyne f- meydl, a hoykhe, un di mame iz geshtanen nebn, ir mame iz geshtanen dernebn

00:18:43.558 --> 00:18:51.849
genumen a revolver, hot geshosn. far vos, far ven, veyst men nisht. un zi hot zikh gegebn a UNK hot zi di m- m- di muter hot gegebn "mayn kosher yidish kind"

00:18:51.849 --> 00:18:53.259
hot zi gegebn a zog.

00:18:54.720 --> 00:18:58.882
un dos iz gevezn. m'hot nisht oyfgedreyt zikh dem kop vayl m'hot moyre gehat.

00:19:02.668 --> 00:19:09.698
vos iz gevezn. der FINKEL- es iz gevezn a Kh- CHILOWICZ, a S.S. man, vos hob ikh ⟨IHNEN⟩ gezogt vos er hot nisht gevust tsu arayngeyn

00:19:09.698 --> 00:19:12.910
bay di tir tsi bay di, nor durkh di fentster geshprungen

00:19:12.642 --> 00:19:15.302
vi hot er geheysn?

00:19:13.570 --> 00:19:15.336
CHILOWICZ hot er geheysn.

00:19:15.460 --> 00:19:16.551
UNK

00:19:23.425 --> 00:19:28.948
ILOV- m'hot im gekhor- geharget nokh di krig. m'hot im gebrengt. in geto hot men im gebrengt keyn Kroke

00:19:28.948 --> 00:19:30.455
un

00:19:30.900 --> 00:19:34.117
dem CHILOWICZ hot men oykhet UNK nisht

00:19:34.309 --> 00:19:35.788
⟨vel⟩ mikh dermanen beser.

00:19:36.233 --> 00:19:41.002
hot men im oykhet gebrengt, iz er geganen eyn mol, iz er gekumen tsu undz in

00:19:41.076 --> 00:19:42.937
vu m'hot gesheylt di kartofl

00:19:42.937 --> 00:19:47.477
un s'iz gevezn zeyer heys, azoy az m'iz nisht gezesn in di shtub, nor s'iz gevezn baym barak

00:19:47.477 --> 00:19:49.617
di gantse mentshn azoy oysgezetst

00:19:49.628 --> 00:19:54.502
un ge- yeder hot gehat UNK do gehat a zak kartofl, un azoy gesheylt di kartofl.

00:19:54.677 --> 00:19:58.113
un er iz dokh nisht gekumen fun VORNE, iz dokh gekumen UNK fun hintn.

00:19:58.272 --> 00:20:00.504
ikh bin gevezn di letste fun hintn

00:20:00.504 --> 00:20:01.505
gezesn.

00:20:02.085 --> 00:20:04.258
un azoy vi iz er arayngekumen

00:20:04.258 --> 00:20:08.013
hot UNK kapo, hot men b- di yidishe, EKSZTAJN hot zi geheysn

00:20:08.013 --> 00:20:10.300
hot gekumen, hot bamerkt az

00:20:10.300 --> 00:20:15.290
az der yeke iz do, hot gezogt "ACHTUNG," hot er shoyn bay mir gezen az ikh tro- halt dos tepele mit

00:20:15.290 --> 00:20:17.360
esn. far vos hob ikh gehaltn dos tepele esn?

00:20:17.360 --> 00:20:21.927
⟨vayl⟩ undz ho'mir gekrign eybik dos letstes esn bay di kokh, hot gekrign dos letstes esn

00:20:21.927 --> 00:20:26.547
hob ikh gehalt s- hob ikh gedarft aropvarfn dos tepele un ikh hob dokh nisht aropgevorfn, hob ikh nokh gehaltn

00:20:26.547 --> 00:20:31.431
hob nish- bald farshtanen az e- az shteyt do a S.S. man far mir

00:20:32.140 --> 00:20:33.799
hot er mikh gezen az ikh

00:20:33.799 --> 00:20:35.458
es, hob gegesn.

00:20:36.038 --> 00:20:41.030
di kapo, zi hot gedarft zogn "her tsu, di mentshn hobn yetst gekrign ⟨heyse⟩ esn."

00:20:41.030 --> 00:20:45.518
neyn. zi hot aleyn moyre gehat, hot gornisht gezogt, hot mikh bald gegebn a ruf

00:20:45.518 --> 00:20:48.012
un ikh bin bald mit im gemuzt mitgeyn

00:20:48.323 --> 00:20:50.308
un iz dernebn gev-

00:20:50.365 --> 00:20:52.401
gevezn mener barakn

00:20:52.558 --> 00:20:56.028
un dort bay di mener barakn hot er mikh genumen in drinen

00:20:56.288 --> 00:20:59.044
un mir oysgetun di hoyzn. ⟨hob ikh⟩ gemuzt knien.

00:20:59.044 --> 00:21:00.900
kh'hob dokh nisht gekent rekhenen

00:21:00.900 --> 00:21:01.583
⟨vayl⟩

00:21:01.583 --> 00:21:04.941
az me krigt mit a rayt baytsh, SIE veysn vos heyst rayt baytsh? UNK a

00:21:04.941 --> 00:21:06.693
⟨geflokhtn⟩ leder

00:21:06.700 --> 00:21:09.930
un do fun hintn iz do aza rundike kleyne shtikl vos me f-

00:21:09.930 --> 00:21:10.820
oyf di ferd

00:21:10.820 --> 00:21:12.730
dos iz a rayt baytsh heyst dos o.

00:21:12.730 --> 00:21:15.657
un mit dem rayt baytsh hot er mir gegebn finef un tsvontsik

00:21:15.657 --> 00:21:20.886
yednfal, ikh hob nisht gekent rekhenen, hot er mir gezogt oyf yekish "az du vest nisht rekhenen, vestu krign mer."

00:21:21.178 --> 00:21:24.817
ober ⟨vi⟩ ikh hob nisht gekent, hob ikh nisht gekent keyn otem khapn, hob ikh nisht gekent rekhenen

00:21:24.891 --> 00:21:30.718
un dos iz gevezn a barak vos zenen gez- -vezn bloyz mener nakht shikht hobn gearbet

00:21:30.718 --> 00:21:38.168
un zey hobn dos do gezen, bahaltenerheyt hot men gezen, hot men shpeter gezogt tsu mayn mame "az ikh bin dos gekent leygn zikh oyf dem kind's plats

00:21:38.168 --> 00:21:39.498
hob ikh mikh geleygt."

00:21:40.095 --> 00:21:42.755
un shpeter hot er mir gezogt "loyf tsu di arbet."

00:21:43.217 --> 00:21:46.293
bin ikh gelofn in dem arbet. nokh dem arbet ruft di mame

00:21:46.293 --> 00:21:48.605
zi hot zikh gezen hot men mikh gen- avekgenumen

00:21:48.605 --> 00:21:50.180
hot zi dokh nisht gevust

00:21:50.625 --> 00:21:53.622
er iz gevezn az ⟨JEMAND⟩ hot avekgenumen, hot er geshosn.

00:21:54.557 --> 00:21:56.039
iz zi gelofn shnel

00:21:56.039 --> 00:21:58.922
tsu ⟨di⟩ blok eltester, tsu dem CHILOWICZn

00:21:58.995 --> 00:22:00.389
iz zi gelofn

00:22:01.965 --> 00:22:03.596
ikh mish mikh shoyn mir di nemen

00:22:03.636 --> 00:22:07.460
tsu FINKELSTEIN iz zi gelofn, shnel gelofn tsu FINKELSTEINen

00:22:07.618 --> 00:22:14.514
un zi hot gezogt "her tsu, hot zi mir, hot men tsugenumen dos kind. geb a kuk vu hot er UNK gefirt, zol men visn vu hot er zi geshosn

00:22:14.605 --> 00:22:17.875
iz er geganen, hot gezukht fun eyn barak dem andern

00:22:17.875 --> 00:22:21.858
iz er gekumen in dem barak arayn, hot er gezen az ⟨JEMAND⟩ shlogt er

00:22:21.858 --> 00:22:23.930
iz er avekgeganen, hot gornisht gezogt.

00:22:24.021 --> 00:22:25.652
hot nokh gevust vu ikh bin.

00:22:25.776 --> 00:22:28.639
ikh bin gelofn shnel arayn in di kokh arayn

00:22:28.948 --> 00:22:30.984
un ikh hob genumen mayn kop

00:22:31.024 --> 00:22:34.742
di mentshn hobn es gezen vos s'iz, hobn genumen mikh untern vaser

00:22:34.742 --> 00:22:38.747
un azoy gelozt loyfn dem vaser oyfn kop, zol ikh kenen tsurik dem otem khapn.

00:22:39.310 --> 00:22:41.430
shpeter hob ikh gekrign akht tog

00:22:41.908 --> 00:22:47.145
fray fun di arbet. bin gevezn ts- fun oybn biz arunter

00:22:47.145 --> 00:22:48.686
bloyz blut.

00:22:49.114 --> 00:22:50.503
veyst ⟨vos heyst⟩ oybn?

00:22:50.503 --> 00:22:52.584
fun danet biz do arunter

00:22:53.012 --> 00:22:54.744
in gantsn mit blut.

00:22:55.088 --> 00:22:57.478
dos gantse hoyt hot zikh oyfgemakht.

00:22:57.720 --> 00:23:01.629
bin ganen nisht in shpitol arayn, nor hob ikh gekrign fray fun di arbet.

00:23:02.715 --> 00:23:06.539
vi lang iz dos gegangen azoy in PLASZOW?

00:23:04.909 --> 00:23:07.957
dos iz gegangen in PLASZOW tsvey yor azoy.

00:23:08.385 --> 00:23:13.205
un in tsvishn, di mentshn zenen ale dort geblibn, oder s'iz geven

00:23:09.820 --> 00:23:10.843
shpe-

00:23:12.199 --> 00:23:18.262
yedes mol geganen veynik, hot men m- yedes mol hot men avekgeshikt zey a bisele

00:23:18.262 --> 00:23:21.542
un yedes mol iz gevorn fargresert di plats.

00:23:22.257 --> 00:23:24.647
fun vu hot men gebrengt di mentshn?

00:23:24.349 --> 00:23:26.749
fun arum un arum, fun di derfer.

00:23:26.749 --> 00:23:33.259
fun Kshanev, fun To- Torne, fun iberal, fun arum un arum hot zikh langzam di getos likvidirt

00:23:33.377 --> 00:23:36.223
un m'hot dort aroyfgebrengt di mentshn alts.

00:23:36.111 --> 00:23:38.197
ales yidn geven?

00:23:37.242 --> 00:23:40.054
ales yidn iz gevezn. ales yidn.

00:23:39.148 --> 00:23:43.107
es iz geven froyen un mener ekster?

00:23:41.967 --> 00:23:46.233
yo, b- s'iz gevezn, hintn iz gevezn, dort gevezn a barg.

00:23:46.233 --> 00:23:48.603
hintn di barg gevezn di mener

00:23:48.603 --> 00:23:53.081
un oybn iz gevezn a gantse barg fun fr- froyen.

00:23:53.897 --> 00:23:58.143
a gantse barg. eyn mol iz gekumen, dos gevezn zumer

00:23:58.538 --> 00:24:02.565
der tog fun di muter bay di yekes, es iz may dakht zikh

00:24:02.655 --> 00:24:07.340
iz gekumen tsun ersht gevezn a, hot geganen ale mener, hobn zey gemuzt geyn

00:24:07.971 --> 00:24:11.070
oyf apel plats, nakedikerheyt, hintn

00:24:11.312 --> 00:24:15.558
un ale mener, froyen oybn, nakedike plats iz gevezn.

00:24:15.598 --> 00:24:17.696
komplet naket. azoy zenen mir geganen

00:24:17.696 --> 00:24:22.072
un s'iz gesh- -kumen fun OSWIECIM, gekumen Mengele

00:24:22.652 --> 00:24:30.965
zey hobn aroysgeshtelt ale kartotekn, zenen mir gevezn ale ayngeshribn, azoy vi hot er gezogt di SCHMUCKSTUCKES ayngeshribn, brengt men di kartoteke far di SCHMUCKSTUCK

00:24:31.326 --> 00:24:33.587
un ale hot er aroysgeshta- yedn

00:24:33.587 --> 00:24:35.407
un Mengele hot gehaltn di

00:24:35.407 --> 00:24:37.407
kartoteke. vemen hot er

00:24:38.093 --> 00:24:41.177
s- z- gezogt oyf rekhts tsi oyf links

00:24:41.177 --> 00:24:44.786
hot er zikh tsugenumen di kartoteke vemen er hot gezogt oyf links.

00:24:45.973 --> 00:24:48.717
do iz gevezn azoy. iz gekumen tsu mayn

00:24:49.095 --> 00:24:50.945
tsu di froyen shpeter aroyf

00:24:51.289 --> 00:24:56.259
bin ikh geganen tsun im, shpeter iz geganen mayn mame fun hintn, ⟨vayl⟩ ikh bin gevezn

00:24:56.259 --> 00:25:00.289
di mame nokh alts shoyn gehongen, un bay mir, ikh bin dokh gevezn nokh a meydl

00:25:00.537 --> 00:25:04.598
a kind, hot zikh nokh alts gut gehaltn, azoy az ikh hob gedekt di mame.

00:25:06.257 --> 00:25:13.034
un zenen geganen azoy, geganen, hot er a ⟨tsi gegebn⟩ di kartoteke, hot men bald gezen az er leygt di kartoteke oyf rekhts.

00:25:13.227 --> 00:25:17.747
hot er gegebn tsurik tsu k- tsu dem kapo, tsu undzere kapo hot er gegebn di kartoteke

00:25:17.747 --> 00:25:21.937
un di andere kartoteke hot er zikh geleygt tsu zikh tsi zayne papirn

00:25:22.153 --> 00:25:26.096
hob ikh gezen az ikh bin nisht oyf yene zayt.

00:25:25.933 --> 00:25:27.243
oyf velkhe zayt?

00:25:26.895 --> 00:25:30.078
oyf di, oyf di linke zayt, ⟨nokh⟩ di rekhte zayt.

00:25:31.063 --> 00:25:35.885
hob ikh geblibn, zenen mir shpeter, iz nokh a por monat, tsi a vokh m-

00:25:35.885 --> 00:25:46.227
vi lang veys ikh nisht vi s'iz ge- gevezn, iz gekumen un hot zikh genumen di ale mentshn vos er hot zikh aroys, ⟨zenen⟩ mir vider gerufn ale oyfn apel plats hintn arunter, shoyn ongetuenerheyt

00:25:46.622 --> 00:25:48.354
un hot ale mentshn

00:25:49.120 --> 00:25:54.210
vos zenen gevezn oyfgeshribn, hot er zey ale tsugenumen keyn OSWIECIM, ale farbrent.

00:25:55.245 --> 00:25:58.102
dos zelbe iz gevezn. iz gevezn tsvey LACHNERS

00:25:58.102 --> 00:25:59.762
yens meydl, nebekh

00:25:59.886 --> 00:26:03.356
hot zi ⟨nem ikh⟩ m- hot ts- er tsugenumen di kartoteke.

00:26:03.598 --> 00:26:06.758
iz gekumen di kapo, iz gevezn di h-

00:26:06.758 --> 00:26:08.838
zi lebt shoyn nisht, di g- di yidishe

00:26:08.838 --> 00:26:11.784
iz gevezn zeyer beyz oyf undz. far vos? vayl bay

00:26:11.784 --> 00:26:14.964
s'iz nisht gevezn keyn familye, zol zayn tsvey tsuzamen.

00:26:14.964 --> 00:26:16.774
veyst farshteyst vos dos heyst?

00:26:16.774 --> 00:26:20.568
un zi hot nisht gekent fartrogn, vayl zi hot oykhet farloyrn kinder

00:26:20.608 --> 00:26:22.967
az undz ze'mir mit tsvey kinder.

00:26:22.967 --> 00:26:26.424
a mame iz mit tsvey kinder tsuzamen. zi hot dos nisht gekent fartrogn.

00:26:26.616 --> 00:26:29.017
demolts iz zi tsugeganen

00:26:29.017 --> 00:26:34.746
"REGINA, gey aroys." "oh," zog ikh, "ikh gey nisht aroys. ikh bin nisht gevezn tsugenumen."

00:26:34.746 --> 00:26:40.228
"gey aroys." "neyn." un azoy vi s'hot z- "az du geyst nisht, gey ikh rufn S.S. man. do hostu."

00:26:40.521 --> 00:26:42.978
un zi iz geganen. zi hot gerufn S.S. man

00:26:43.153 --> 00:26:47.883
un azoy, yene hot zikh nisht ongerufn. zi hot dokh oykhet ⟨vider az zi hot⟩ dokh gevolt lebn, dos meydele

00:26:47.883 --> 00:26:52.411
hot zikh nisht ongerufn. zi iz tsugeganen tsu mir, vayl zi hot gevust az ikh heys oykhet LACHNER

00:26:52.570 --> 00:26:59.755
vayl beyde zenen mir gevezn in dem zelbn barak, un beyde iz gevezn oyfn zelbn plats tsu arbetn. hob ikh gezogt "neyn, ikh gey nisht aroys," hot zi geheysn TOSHKE.

00:26:59.755 --> 00:27:01.828
"TOSHKE, ikh gey nisht aroys.

00:27:01.986 --> 00:27:04.376
ikh gey nisht UNK dos bin nisht ikh."

00:27:04.568 --> 00:27:08.108
nu, azoy vi hob ikh gezen d- az ikh hob nisht keyn breyre vider

00:27:08.108 --> 00:27:10.398
hob ikh mikh gegebn a drey avek

00:27:10.398 --> 00:27:13.186
un bin ikh tsugeganen tsu andern

00:27:13.186 --> 00:27:15.066
plats vos zenen geshtanen froyen

00:27:15.066 --> 00:27:17.825
un dos andere meydl nebekh aroysgeganen.

00:27:20.498 --> 00:27:21.116
UNK

00:27:22.894 --> 00:27:27.227
vi azoy iz dos gekumen az ir zent fun dort avekgeforn?

00:27:27.227 --> 00:27:29.604
az m'hot aykh fun dort avekgeshikt

00:27:30.623 --> 00:27:32.254
fun PLASZOW?

00:27:30.943 --> 00:27:32.928
oh, dos hot nokh zeyer lang gedoyert.

00:27:33.205 --> 00:27:38.734
dos UNK zeyer lang gedoyert, un der tate nebekh UNK hot men im oykhet gevolt nemen in

00:27:38.757 --> 00:27:40.219
keyn

00:27:41.035 --> 00:27:44.454
keyn RABKA, hot men im gevolt nemen tsu gr-

00:27:43.482 --> 00:27:45.028
tsu arbetn?

00:27:44.562 --> 00:27:45.906
tsu arbetn.

00:27:46.013 --> 00:27:47.976
hot er nebekh nisht gevolt geyn.

00:27:47.976 --> 00:27:50.327
tsu arbetn keyn, keyn RABKA

00:27:51.447 --> 00:27:55.862
vayl er hot gevust s'iz oykh mit di familye un blaybn aleyn nisht

00:27:55.969 --> 00:27:57.999
un ikh bin gevezn krank

00:27:57.999 --> 00:27:59.169
bin gelegn

00:27:59.169 --> 00:28:00.449
in shpitol.

00:28:00.449 --> 00:28:03.559
kh'hob gehat a urin BLASE, ETS- ERKALTET

00:28:04.120 --> 00:28:10.172
iz er geganen, UNK antlofn, azoy vi m'hot genumen zayn transport, iz er antlofn fun dem transport

00:28:10.600 --> 00:28:16.264
un iz gelofn in dem ABTEILUNG vu iz di ⟨shpiteler⟩ ABTEILUNG, hot gevust az ikh bin dort

00:28:16.573 --> 00:28:18.929
un er hot zikh bahaltn in a korb arayn.

00:28:17.907 --> 00:28:19.200
vu iz dos geven?

00:28:19.020 --> 00:28:20.502
oykhet in PLASZOW.

00:28:20.050 --> 00:28:21.326
in PLASZOW.

00:28:20.502 --> 00:28:24.701
s'iz gevezn a gantse ⟨shpiteler⟩, ales iz dort gevezn.

00:28:25.146 --> 00:28:26.181
un

00:28:26.181 --> 00:28:31.445
un iz er gelofn dortn in kerb- korb, un bay nakht kumt er tsu mir tsu geyn, zogt er

00:28:31.445 --> 00:28:40.279
kh'ho- m'hot fartseylt di mayse. m'hot im ⟨oyssekretirt⟩, un er muz, hot gedarft geyn in a transport, un der transport iz nokh nisht geganen. er vet do lign a tsvey tog.

00:28:40.279 --> 00:28:44.760
vos hob ikh gehat fun shtikele broyt hob ikh im gegebn, vayl er iz dokh gelegn in a korb.

00:28:44.760 --> 00:28:46.692
ikh bin dokh gevezn in shpitol

00:28:46.692 --> 00:28:51.364
un krankerheyt bin ikh aroysgeganen tsu mayn mame fartseyln az der tate iz do

00:28:51.538 --> 00:28:55.180
iz tomer vet zayn der transport vet shoyn avekgeyn

00:28:55.180 --> 00:28:59.559
zol zi UNK kumen do un do UNK, zol men im zogn az er ken aroysgeyn

00:28:59.559 --> 00:29:03.229
iz ⟨er⟩ takesh azoy gevezn. iz dort gebahaltn gevezn di tsvey tog.

00:29:03.229 --> 00:29:06.584
ikh hob shoyn yedes mol tsugetrogn a shtikele broyt tsu esn

00:29:06.777 --> 00:29:09.285
iz er dort azoy gelegn. shpeter

00:29:10.050 --> 00:29:13.260
az der transport iz avekgeganen

00:29:13.260 --> 00:29:18.080
iz er aroysgeganen, hot er zikh tsugeshtelt vider tsu zayn barak, un azoy

00:29:17.138 --> 00:29:19.312
lomir zikh do opshteln a minut.

00:29:18.403 --> 00:29:19.007
yo.

00:29:19.312 --> 00:29:21.084
antshuldikt, ober s'iz fertik.
